translations: 大教堂；修道院附属的教堂

sentences.sentence: Other items inspired by the Forbidden City have also become hits, such as earphones and umbrellas that look like the necklaces and hats worn by the minsters of the Qing Dynasty (1644-1911).
sentences.translation: 其他的一些饰品也成为了热销品，例如耳机、雨伞以及清朝(1644 - 1911年)官员们穿戴的项链和帽子。
